HEADWORD: Burmannia
<hw>Burmannia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the type genus of the
Burmanniaceae; slender herbs of warm regions with leaves resembling
scales and flowers with a 3-angled or 3-winged perianth.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Burmannia</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
